# GitHub: use SSH

For this project, **always use SSH URLs** for GitHub, not HTTPS.

- **Clone:** `git clone git@github.com:org/repo.git`
- **Submodule add:** `git submodule add git@github.com:org/repo.git path`
- **Remote add / documentation:** Prefer `git@github.com:org/repo.git` in any instructions or commands you suggest.

Do not suggest `https://github.com/org/repo.git` for git operations. The system is configured for SSH access.
